<h2 id="orgheadline1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> hunspell 설치</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<p>
가장 편한 방법은 Windows Package Manager인 <a href="https://chocolatey.org/">Chocolatey</a> 를 사용하는 것입니다:
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">


<pre><code class="lang-posh">&gt; choco install hunspell.portable
</code></pre>

