<div id="outline-container-orgheadline2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline2"><span class="section-number-2">2</span> init</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">
<p>
Emacs의 <a href="http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/InitFile">init file</a> 에 다음을 추가합니다:
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">


<pre><code class="lang-emacs">(require 'ispell)

(cond ((eq system-type 'gnu/linux) 
    (progn
      (setq ispell-program-name "hunspell")
     ) 
  ((eq system-type 'windows-nt)
    (progn
       (add-to-list 'exec-path "C:/ProgramData/Chocolatey/bin/")
       (setq ispell-program-name (locate-file "hunspell"
                                              exec-path exec-suffixes 'file-executable-p))
     ))))

(setq ispell-really-hunspell t)

(add-to-list 'ispell-dictionary-alist '("en_US"
                                        "[[:alpha:]]"
                                        "[^[:alpha:]]"
                                        "[']"
                                        t
                                        ("-d" "en_US")
                                        nil
                                        utf-8))
(add-to-list 'ispell-dictionary-alist '("korean"
                                        "[&#44032;-&#55203;]"
                                        "[^&#44032;-&#55203;]"
                                        "[0-9a-zA-Z]"
                                        nil
                                        ("-d" "ko_KR")
                                        nil
                                        utf-8))

;; &#54620;&#44397;&#50612;&#47484; &#44592;&#48376; &#49324;&#51204;&#51004;&#47196; &#51648;&#51221;
(setq ispell-dictionary "korean")
; (setq ispell-dictionary "en_US")
</code></pre>

</div>
